{"tid":1741940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【自救錦囊】現仍留在理大的無辜學生請入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2019-11-20T14:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:25:55.000Z","uid":278463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"29d88e2fee464af7be8e0dca70edd848d5f371a7","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n首先，學生們如果是無辜的，就不要自首，因為只有罪犯才會自首！ <br />\n<br />\n除非已確認犯了嚴重紀律問題被大學紀律委員會開會正式開除校籍，否則已交了學費的正常學生有權留在學校。因為大學已收了學生的學費，所以就算校長亦無權趕學生走。<br />\n<br />\n現時尖東商業區街頭企咗好多黑警甴，等班外面班黑警甴散咗先走啦，佢地冇可能永遠企在那裡阻住尖東商廈/酒店/商場嘅人返工和開舖，學生們暫時留在理大校內最安全。不要冒險出逃！ </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>學生可先在 圖書館、課室、飯堂等 溫書和休息，如果黑警甴真係夠膽漠視國際譴責攻入校園，上到法庭都大把抗辯理由話係無辜，告你地唔入的，總好過現在就貿貿然衝出去被癲狗拉。身處理大的非學校人員萬一被捕時可話自己之前入去理大搵朋友但無辜被困。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong>下星期理工大學周邊應該會通返車可以行人了，到時黑警甴封路駐守嘅數目會大減。 <br />\n留守嘅同學們在裡面最多住到過埋農曆年，我唔信理工大學下年一月底過完農曆年仲唔俾學生上課開學！<br />\n<br />\n港共政權現在怕國際譴責連強攻入去理工大學都唔敢，更加唔敢餓死人，所以如果唔夠嘢食就提前一個星期前向外舉牌話入面唔夠糧食，要黑警俾醫護或記者帶糧食入去。<br />\n如果裡面餓死人或發生其他人道災難嘅話，柒婆就肯定要被國際通緝拉上國際法庭審判了，除非佢想成世留喺大灣區唔出去。<br />\n</strong></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ee26f82cd18b3768bb72680529da9b9bdb5625f2","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"a8d7cf8a1d94ad196063e23f1207a3241863aa51","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"da9f1eff17fec5825831cae9a79fb5c990cc089c","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:23:39.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"8a607f1cef454d575aadbb1b52680ec04db85429","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"f0e010a2354ddc41bdfc2b790a1df86daf771b91","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"d919fb6366946e220745cef6b6e4b24180db3479","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"242ff39ad702a295129a3f51d67f54614d4f1746","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"c4bba52a5fe798c2a85f44453353eaf9d27410c3","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"94c8180ccdd6ae841401fde31fb79f0eb799def7","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"ea622a3990cb629706793e276d6c915b15138276","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:25:31.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"c4577c4593f8749f562ea450b5121cbb990fc54e","tid":1741940,"uid":278463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人加油！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}